fields.title: Minor Hand Injury During Machine Maintenance
fields.description: During routine maintenance of a conveyor belt, an employee sustained a minor hand injury due to improper handling of tools. No machinery damage occurred and production was briefly paused.
fields.immediate_action_taken: First aid was administered immediately, and the employee was taken to the onsite medical room for observation. Work was stopped temporarily in the affected area.
fields.environmental_factors: Noise and limited working space near the equipment
fields.equipment_involved: Conveyor belt system and handheld maintenance tools

fields.problem_statement: 8D Problem Solving for: Minor Hand Injury During Machine Maintenance
